Package: hdxr
Title: Connect to Humanitarian Data Exchange. Extract Useful Information
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: person("Callum", "Taylor", email = "callum.taylor@glasgow.ac.uk", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows easy interaction with the humanitarian data exchange (https://data.humdata.org)
    in a reproducible workflow. You can currently download information about each dataset and the resources they contain, 
    extract further information about resources, plus load csvs and shapefiles into your environment.
    It wraps existing packages to interact with hdx (ckanr, httr, jsonlite), tidyverse features to interact with the data, 
    plus sf for spatial data.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
URL: https://github.com/callumgwtaylor/hdxr
BugReports: https://github.com/callumgwtaylor/hdxr/issues
License: MIT
